                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18190707-70-defend696 t18190707-70-deflabel375"></join>. On the 10th of May she left - next morning, I missed these things. On the 11th of June I met her in Oxford-street - she ran away; I followed her and secured her with one of my gowns on. As we were taking her to Marlborough-street she said she could produce duplicates of every thing; they were found on her. I went to the pawnbroker's, and got the property.</p>
